original: Åren, Sven Magnus, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 9/6/15 i Askersund av med. lic. Ture Å. O: Herta Enemark. — Stud:ex. 34, tandl :kand. 39’, tandläk:-ex. 45. Distr :tandläk. i Lerum 44-46, skoltandläk. i Gbg fr. 46.
translated: Years, Sven Magnus, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 9/6/15 in Askersund to medical licentiate Ture Å. His spouse: Herta Enemark. — High school graduate in 1934, dental student in 1939, dental exam in 1945. District dentist in Lerum from 1944-1946, school dentist in Gothenburg from 1946.
